---
import MainLayout from '../layouts/MainLayout.astro';
---

<MainLayout title="Visitor Visa Services" description="Visitor visa and eTA requirements for travel to Canada">
  <section class="page-header section-padding">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <span class="gold-text uppercase-label">Visa Services</span>
      <h1>Visitor Visa</h1>
      <p class="subtitle">A visitor visa is required for certain foreign nationals who wish to visit or transit through Canada.</p>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="visitor-visa-content section-padding">
    <div class="container">
      <div class="content-grid">
        <!-- Visitor Visa Requirements -->
        <div class="glass-card content-section">
          <div class="section-icon"> visa</div>
          <h2>Visitor Visa Requirements</h2>
          <p>Depending on your nationality, you may need to obtain a temporary resident visa. Visitors from countries that do not require a visa (except the U.S.) must apply for an eTA before boarding.</p>
          <div class="highlight-box">
            <h3>Eligibility Criteria:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>A valid passport or travel document</li>
              <li>Good health (a medical exam may be necessary)</li>
              <li>Proof of ties to your home country (job, property, family) to demonstrate intent to return</li>
              <li>Sufficient funds for your stay (amount varies depending on trip details)</li>
              <li>A letter of invitation from a Canadian resident (if applicable)</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Visa Types and Process -->
        <div class="glass-card content-section">
          <div class="section-icon"> description</div>
          <h2>Visa Issuance & Process</h2>
          <p>Approved applicants receive a visa, either single or multiple entries, to use for travel. The process involves completing an online application, submitting supporting documents, and paying fees. Processing times vary based on your country and individual circumstances.</p>
          <div class="highlight-box">
            <h3>Application Support:</h3>
            <ul>
              <li>Preparing detailed legal submissions</li>
              <li>Reviewing supporting documentation</li>
              <li>Addressing inadmissibility concerns</li>
              <li>Handling extensions and refusals effectively</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Extending Your Stay & Refusals -->
        <div class="glass-card content-section">
          <div class="section-icon"> update</div>
          <h2>Extending Your Stay & Refusals</h2>
          <p>If you wish to stay longer, you must apply for an extension at least 30 days before your current visa expires. A visitor record will allow you to remain legally in the country with a new expiry date. If your application is pending, your status remains valid (maintained status).</p>
          <p>A refusal can be disappointing, but it's not the end. Understanding the reasons and working with an immigration expert can increase your chances of success upon reapplication.</p>
        </div>

        <!-- eTA Requirements -->
        <div class="glass-card content-section">
          <div class="section-icon"> electronic</div>
          <h2>eTA Requirements</h2>
          <p>An eTA is mandatory for visa-exempt travelers arriving by air. It is electronically linked to your passport and valid for up to five years or until your passport expires. While it facilitates entry, it does not guarantee admission—border officials decide at the port of entry.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="cta-section section-padding bg-darker">
    <div class="container text-center">
      <h2>Need Help With Your Visa Application?</h2>
      <p class="subtitle">Our experienced immigration team is ready to assist you at every step.</p>
      <div class="cta-buttons">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-primary">Contact Us Today</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</MainLayout>

<style>
  /* [Your existing styles remain exactly the same] */
  :global(body) {
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #faf8ff 0%, #f5f0ff 50%, #fdf2f8 100%);
    min-height: 100vh;
  }
  .page-header {
    background: linear-gradient(rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5), rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5)), url('/visitor-vissa.webp') center/cover no-repeat;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--border-light);
    padding-top: 150px;
    padding-bottom: 80px;
  }
  .page-header h1 {
    color: white;
  }
  .uppercase-label {
    display: inline-block;
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-weight: 600;
    letter-spacing: 0.15em;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 0.9rem;
    color: white;
  }
  .subtitle {
    margin-top: 20px;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: white;
    max-width: 700px;
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
  }
  .content-grid {
    display: grid;
    gap: 40px;
    max-width: 900px;
    margin: 0 auto;
  }
  .content-section {
    padding: 40px;
    border-radius: 16px;
    background: var(--card-bg);
    border: 1px solid var(--card-border);
    box-shadow: var(--card-shadow);
    position: relative;
    overflow: hidden;
  }
  .content-section::before {
    content: '';
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 0;
    right: 0;
    bottom: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.03), rgba(219, 39, 119, 0.03));
    z-index: -1;
  }
  .section-icon {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    color: var(--primary-purple);
    opacity: 0.8;
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .content-section h2 {
    font-size: 2rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-main);
    font-weight: 600;
  }
  .content-section p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.7;
    margin-bottom: 24px;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .highlight-box {
    background: rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.05);
    border: 1px solid rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.1);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 24px;
    margin-top: 24px;
  }
  .highlight-box h3 {
    color: var(--primary-purple);
    margin-bottom: 16px;
    font-size: 1.3rem;
  }
  .highlight-box ul {
    list-style: none;
    padding: 0;
    margin: 0;
  }
  .highlight-box li {
    position: relative;
    padding-left: 24px;
    margin-bottom: 12px;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    line-height: 1.6;
  }
  .highlight-box li::before {
    content: 'check_circle';
    position: absolute;
    left: 0;
    color: var(--primary-purple);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    font-family: 'Material Icons';
    font-weight: normal;
    font-style: normal;
  }
  .bg-darker {
    background-color: var(--background);
    border-top: 1px solid var(--border-light);
  }
  .cta-section h2 {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    margin-bottom: 20px;
    color: var(--text-main);
  }
  .cta-buttons {
    display: flex;
    gap: 20px;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    margin-top: 40px;
  }
  .btn {
    padding: 16px 32px;
    border-radius: 8px;
    text-decoration: none;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
    display: inline-block;
    font-size: 1.1rem;
  }
  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--primary-gradient);
    color: white;
    border: none;
  }
  .btn-primary:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 25px rgba(124, 58, 237, 0.3);
  }
  @media (max-width: 992px) {
    .page-header {
      padding-top: 120px;
      padding-bottom: 70px;
    }
    .content-section {
      padding: 32px;
    }
    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.8rem;
    }
    .section-icon {
      font-size: 2rem;
    }
    .content-section p {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 2.2rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 768px) {
    .page-header {
      padding-top: 100px;
      padding-bottom: 60px;
    }
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
    .uppercase-label {
      font-size: 0.8rem;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .content-grid {
      gap: 24px;
    }
    .content-section {
      padding: 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
    }
    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .section-icon {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content-section p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-bottom: 16px;
    }
    .content-section li {
      padding-left: 20px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .content-section li::before {
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      padding: 16px;
      margin-top: 16px;
    }
    .highlight-box h3 {
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      margin-bottom: 12px;
    }
    .highlight-box li {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .cta-section {
      padding: 60px 0;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.75rem;
    }
    .cta-buttons {
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 16px;
      margin-top: 30px;
    }
    .btn {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 280px;
      padding: 14px 28px;
      font-size: 1rem;
    }
  }

  @media (max-width: 480px) {
    .page-header {
      padding-top: 80px;
      padding-bottom: 50px;
    }
    .page-header h1 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .subtitle {
      font-size: 0.9rem;
    }
    .content-section {
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .content-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.3rem;
    }
    .highlight-box {
      padding: 14px;
    }
    .cta-section h2 {
      font-size: 1.5rem;
    }
    .btn {
      padding: 12px 24px;
      font-size: 0.95rem;
    }
  }
</style>